name: Shelby Yardley
bio: Actress slash Gamer slash 50 other things ♡

social_posts.post_text: The last couple months? Whew. There’s been a LOT of bad.. Funerals, stitches, panic attacks, tears, anxiety, failures, etc. These photos are a much happier version of what it’s been like, the moments that got me through it ❤️

How to sum up this year.. There really aren’t enough words or photo slots to explain it. Simply said, it was a rollercoaster. The highest of highs accompanied by the lowest of lows. There are many things that were AMAZING about this year, and there were other things that were absolutely terrible. I’m going to take all of it and use tonight to reflect on how I want to use it for the next year 💭 Wishing you all an amazing NYE! #2022recap
6 years together, 2 married. Thank you for doing life with me 🥹❤️ I love you forever.
I finally left my house yesterday, but only because this was important ⚠️
The exact spot B and I met 7 years ago ❤️‍🔥
da ba dee da ba diii 💙

We are so proud to finally share our project Calabasas Criminals with the world. It’s been a journey with this one.. pitching a TV show is nothing short of a monster of a task but we have had so much fun doing it. This project has had to stay under the radar for over 2 years but we have decided it finally deserves a festival run! Keep an eye out for updates and maybe even a glimpse into the world of these four characters 💰
I see a lot of pink, black, & bows in my 2024
